    "name": "JeliWave",
    "steam_appid": 3206640,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206640/extras/df38a14d19a046fc7ebe41723899a383.avif?t=1736362870\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206640/extras_big/df38a14d19a046fc7ebe41723899a383.avif?t=1736362870 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >JeliWave is a linear 3D platformer with the visual appearance of retro games from the 90s. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Swing your way through various worlds, unlock new abilities and master the art of Jeli's grapple! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206640/extras/9f19673b61e64c910c83737c084db8c3.poster.avif?t=1736362870\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206640/extras/9f19673b61e64c910c83737c084db8c3.webm?t=1736362870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206640/extras/9f19673b61e64c910c83737c084db8c3.mp4?t=1736362870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You take the role of Jeli, a Slime character with extendable arms, and you must navigate your way through various stages of different themed worlds! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn the mechanics and blaze through the levels to see how fast you can complete stages, or collect the blobs throughout the stages for nice bonus unlocks! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206640/extras/4fc65079a322494a333c14905f245a6b.poster.avif?t=1736362870\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206640/extras/4fc65079a322494a333c14905f245a6b.webm?t=1736362870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206640/extras/4fc65079a322494a333c14905f245a6b.mp4?t=1736362870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge yourself and try to get good times on stages for a high rank! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you get the fabled X Rank? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206640/extras/f748d6167f7ca30a5500d7c607cf40ac.poster.avif?t=1736362870\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206640/extras/f748d6167f7ca30a5500d7c607cf40ac.webm?t=1736362870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206640/extras/f748d6167f7ca30a5500d7c607cf40ac.mp4?t=1736362870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
